 <body ><br><h1 class="pHead1" >
assert_implication
</h1>    
<a name="wp3680245"> </a><p class="pBody" >
Ensures that a specified consequent expression is TRUE if the specified antecedent expression is TRUE.  </p>    <div align="left" class="tbl">
