</table>
</div>
	
  <p class="pBody" >
</p>    
<a name="wp3680420"> </a><p class="pBody" >
Ensures that <code class="cCodeBody">q_not_full</code> is TRUE at each rising edge of <code class="cCodeBody">clk</code> for which <code class="cCodeBody">q_valid</code> is TRUE.  </p>    <div align="left"><img src="images/ovl_checkersa22.gif" height="86" width="300" border="0" vspace="0" hspace="100" />  </div>	
